內容來自 Udacity 上 <a href="https://www.udacity.com/course/intro-to-relational-databases--ud197">Intro to Relational Databases</a> 的免費課程與我自己整理的資訊。</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">sqlite3</span>

<span class="n">conn</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">sqlite3</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">connect</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"Cookies"</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1"># 連接 SQLite 資料庫
</span><span class="n">cursor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">conn</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">cursor</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="c1"># 獲得連接的游標
</span>
<span class="c1"># 要下的 SQL 指令
</span><span class="n">cursor</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span>
    <span class="s">"select host_key from cookies limit 10;"</span>
<span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">results</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">cursor</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">fetchall</span><span class="p">()</span>

<span class="k">print</span> <span class="n">resutls</span> <span class="c1"># 結果為 turple
</span>
<span class="n">conn</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="c1"># 每次都要記得 close 連線
</span></code></pre></div></div>
